    <!-- ==========================
        Founder Content
    =========================== -->
    <section class="about-layout2 pb-0">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            <div class="heading-layout2">
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-40">About South Asian Liver Institute</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="about__text bg-white">
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Think Liver, Think SALi. We provide the best liver care.</h3>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-30">South Asian Liver Institute (SALi) is India's premier destination for comprehensive liver care, established with a vision to bring world-class hepatology and transplant services to South Asia. We have performed over 650 successful liver transplants achieving a 91% survival rate, and over 250 complex liver cancer resections with 98% survival, treating tens of thousands of patients with various liver diseases.</p>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-30">Our flagship center in Hyderabad, along with partner hospitals across major cities in India, ensures that expert liver care is accessible to patients from all regions. From our state-of-the-art transplant unit to advanced diagnostic facilities, SALi represents the gold standard in liver healthcare.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
            <img src="/assets/images/about/1.jpg" alt="SALi Facility" class="w-100 mb-30" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-50">
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            <div class="about__text bg-white">
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Our Mission</h3>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-30">To provide affordable, accessible, and world-class liver care to every patient in need, regardless of their geographic or economic background. We strive to advance the field of hepatology through clinical excellence, research, and education.</p>
              
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Our Vision</h3>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-30">To be South Asia's most trusted and advanced liver care institute, recognized globally for clinical outcomes, patient satisfaction, research contributions, and training of the next generation of liver specialists.</p>
              
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Our Values</h3>
              <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-40 pl-40">
                <li><strong>Patient-Centered Care:</strong> Every decision is made with the patient's best interest at heart</li>
                <li><strong>Clinical Excellence:</strong> Maintaining the highest standards of medical practice</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Adopting the latest technologies and treatment approaches</li>
                <li><strong>Compassion:</strong> Treating every patient and family with empathy and respect</li>
                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Operating with transparency and ethical principles</li>
                <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Teamwork across disciplines for optimal patient outcomes</li>
              </ul>
              
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Our Achievements</h3>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                  <div class="counter-item text-center mb-30">
                    <h3 class="counter__number color-primary">650+</h3>
                    <p class="counter__desc">Liver Transplants</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                  <div class="counter-item text-center mb-30">
                    <h3 class="counter__number color-primary">91%</h3>
                    <p class="counter__desc">Transplant Survival Rate</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                  <div class="counter-item text-center mb-30">
                    <h3 class="counter__number color-primary">250+</h3>
                    <p class="counter__desc">Complex Cancer Resections</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                  <div class="counter-item text-center mb-30">
                    <h3 class="counter__number color-primary">98%</h3>
                    <p class="counter__desc">Cancer Surgery Survival</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Our Services</h3>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-20">SALi offers a complete spectrum of liver care services including:</p>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-40 pl-40">
                    <li>Living Donor Liver Transplantation</li>
                    <li>Deceased Donor Liver Transplantation</li>
                    <li>Pediatric Liver Transplantation</li>
                    <li>Comprehensive Hepatology Services</li>
                    <li>Liver Cancer Treatment (HCC)</li>
                    <li>Interventional Radiology (TACE, RFA)</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-40 pl-40">
                    <li>Advanced Endoscopy (ERCP, EUS)</li>
                    <li>Laparoscopic Liver Surgery</li>
                    <li>Critical Care & ICU Services</li>
                    <li>Fatty Liver Management Programs</li>
                    <li>Cirrhosis Care & Monitoring</li>
                    <li>Hepatitis B & C Treatment</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="heading__title mb-30">Why Choose SALi?</h3>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-20">
                <strong>Expert Team:</strong> Our multidisciplinary team includes some of India's most experienced liver transplant surgeons, hepatologists, interventional radiologists, and critical care specialists, many trained at premier international institutions.
              </p>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-20">
                <strong>Cutting-Edge Technology:</strong> We invest in the latest medical equipment including advanced imaging systems, minimally invasive surgical tools, and state-of-the-art ICU facilities.
              </p>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-20">
                <strong>Comprehensive Care:</strong> From initial consultation to post-transplant follow-up, we provide end-to-end care with dedicated coordinators guiding patients through every step.
              </p>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-20">
                <strong>Proven Outcomes:</strong> Our transplant success rates match international standards, with one-year patient survival exceeding 90% and five-year survival above 80%.
              </p>
              <p class="heading__desc mb-30">
                <strong>Patient Support Programs:</strong> LICAP (Liver Cancer Awareness Program), Liver Line helpline, and Ascites Club provide ongoing education and support to patients and families.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
